(42, 22, 38, 43, 18, 36, 36, 'two swords', 'Swords and Kingdoms Connection', 'This connection highlights the contrast between physical weapons and the nature of Jesus'' kingdom. While the disciples mention swords, Jesus clarifies that his kingdom does not rely on worldly means of defense or conflict.', 'theme', 0.33499999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
