(42, 22, 38, 49, 6, 10, 18, 'two swords', 'Spiritual Warfare and Preparation', 'This connection highlights the theme of readiness for conflict. In Luke, the mention of swords suggests a need for preparation, while Ephesians emphasizes putting on the whole armor of God to stand against spiritual adversaries.', 'theme', 0.33499999999999996, 'medium', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(42, 22, 38, 52, 5, 8, 8, NULL, 'Swords and Spiritual Armor', 'This connection highlights the theme of preparedness in both passages. The mention of ''swords'' in Luke suggests a need for readiness, while ''breastplate'' and ''helmet'' in Thessalonians symbolize spiritual armor for protection.', 'theme', 0.321, 'medium', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(42, 22, 38, 60, 5, 9, 9, 'It is enough', 'Resisting Afflictions in Faith', 'This connection highlights the theme of preparedness in the face of challenges. In Luke 22:38, the mention of swords symbolizes readiness, while 1 Peter 5:9 emphasizes resisting afflictions steadfastly in faith.', 'theme', 0.321, 'medium', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
